  "html_url": "https://github.com/algolia/instantsearch/issues/827",
  "title": "urlSync perf issue on Chrome",
  "body": "Chrome has troubles updating the URL as often as it can get when typing in the searchbox, resulting in a very slow/laggy search experience.\n\nWe don't really need the URL to be updated at each keystroke (who wants to click the back button 10 times after typing a 10-letter query?), so the best solution could be to sync the URL only when the searchbox is blurred?\n\nOr at least debounce the URL update to avoid changing it too often.\n",
